---
// Import Tailwind CSS for styling (optional)
import 'tailwindcss/tailwind.css';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600">About Neon Farm</h1>
    <p class="mt-4">
      Welcome to Neon Farm, where the future of farming glows bright. Our mission is to revolutionize agriculture through innovative technologies and sustainable practices. At Neon Farm, we believe in growing food that not only nourishes the body but also the soul.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2">
      Our journey began in [Year], with a small team of visionaries who dreamed of a greener planet. Today, we are proud to be at the forefront of the agricultural tech industry, pioneering new ways to farm, harvest, and distribute the freshest produce.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2">
      From vertical farming to hydroponics, we're exploring every avenue to make our farm as efficient and eco-friendly as possible. Join us as we light up the world, one neon crop at a time.
    </p>
    <a href="/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline mt-4 inline-block">Back to Home</a>
  </div>
</Layout>